This week on the Major Issues Podcast, Spooky Season continues as the hosts dive into DCeased — DC Comics’ apocalyptic six-issue series from Tom Taylor, Trevor Hairsine, and Stefano Gaudiano. When a corrupted version of the Anti-Life Equation infects Earth through social media, the world’s greatest heroes and villains are turned into mindless, murderous versions of themselves. As Superman, Wonder Woman, Batman, and the rest of the Justice League struggle to save what’s left of humanity, the question becomes: can even gods survive the end of the world? Join the discussion as the hosts break down the horror, heart, and heroism that make DCeased one of DC’s most shocking and emotional Elseworld tales.

Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

